
BinProlog
	:-(Goal).   ... execute Goal after everything is included
	:-##(Goal). ... execute Goal immediately *when* including
        		Remark: the rest of file after ##/2 is ignored!
        :-[file]    ... include using already defined method (e.g. consult/1)
                        default: include everything into 1 file
	:-consult(file) ... include file by file

